rust referencesedit  httpwwwterrafirmacomaboutterrafirmahtml  a b hands edges toward nomura exit door may    guy hands financial news june    the man who loves disasters business week june    nomuras guy hands dealmaker extraordinaire global finance november   a b uk terra firma to seal debut deal altassets jun    hands seen dropping plans for major bank role in new fund altassets jul    cowell alan world business briefing  europe britain nomura investor to open fund new york times november    nomura signs agreement with guy hands to invest in terra firma altassets jan    a b uk terra firma announces final close on ebn altassets mar    guy hands’ terra firma holds first close on debut independent fund altassets nov    guy hands holds second closing for terra firma fund on ebn altassets nov    a b terra firma closes € billion fund private equity international jun    battle of the bands citigroup is up next new york times february    terra firma  annual review  private equity is still not showing its hand the telegraph   ilpa private equity principles institutional limited partners association  emi accepts  billion bid from terra firma new york times may     billion private equity buyout wins support at emi new york times may    terra firma said to unveil emi plans new york times november    profile british music giant emi bbc news  january  retrieved  march    stones sign onealbum record deal bbc news  january  retrieved  march    jenison david stones shine a light on emis woes e online retrieved  march    stones ditching emi for universal bbc news  july  retrieved  may    tapper james  may  joss stone to sacrifice £m to free herself from emi album deal daily mail mail online retrieved  may    a b emi set to cut up to  jobs bbc news  january  retrieved  march    emi’s new boss sees cracks in music world new york times june    guy hands sees no sunshine ahead new york times november    give guy credit for emis brits success london evening standard  feb   terra firma w